## Tooling Restriction — patch-tool.jar

The `patch-tool.jar` binary included in this repository is provided
**exclusively for use with the practice targets and lab exercises in this
project**. You may NOT use `patch-tool.jar` to instrument, modify, repackage,
or analyze any application other than:

- The target APKs provided in `materials/targets/`
- Applications you have **built yourself** for local testing
- Applications for which you hold **explicit written authorization** to assess

Redistribution of `patch-tool.jar` outside the context of this repository is
not permitted. Use of the tool against any application without proper
authorization may violate applicable computer misuse and anti-circumvention
laws (see Chapter 2 of the book).

